cognitive_id_specific_instructions.6f42a946-a936-45f9-9b2b-dbc1ad80b936:
Tu hi cawlcanghnak tuahnak caan a si. Tuah hlan ahcun, dah hi nganpi ah um khawh:

  • Cawlcanghnak cu biahalnak 31 an i a si.
  • Na duh zat in caan na lak khawh a si. Asinain, tampi cu 15 minute chung i an ti hna.
  • Lungretheihnak um loin cawlcanghnak hna kha na lungthin dihlak in na pek khawhnak ding hmun dai tein na kawl awk a si.
  • Na herh ahcun biahalnak kha na hrial khawh, asinain biahalnak pakhat cio kha a phi pek khawh i zuam.
  • Cawlcanghnak cu voikhat tthutnak ah lim in tuah khawh.

cognitive_instructions_disability_text: Na hmanhnak ah hriamhmi loh thil pawl kha na hmanhrawh?
cognitive_instructions_step_1_text:
Na duh mi thilri hna cu khua hman hlawmhmi a si.

Hi screen pakhat ah, a cunglei '?' tawk mi shape chungin shape hrawng lohna a um. Hi hrawng ah, a cunglei '?' kha a hrial khawh mi shape 4 a um i a phan khawh.

Tuah hlan i, grid chungin hrawng mi shape kha a phan khawh tawn, confirm button tla in hawi i, laingngeih thilri hna kha kan theih. Skip hna kha laih in ummi, a si maw a si.
cognitive_instructions_step_2_heading: He hi zangfah pakhat an si
cognitive_instructions_step_2_text: Hi grid ah triangle, pentagon, le arrow cu row le column pakhat cio ah ummi a si. A neimi thilri pakhat cu, a zawng tawn a si mi black, blue, le white a si i, an tampi hna cu zangfah zawn he an ttuanmi. Grid cu a hung kaizerh piak dingmi thilri cu a cunglei ah bawmhnak khat a ummi a si.
cognitive_instructions_step_4_html:
Tu hi cawlcanghnak tuahnak caan a si. Tuah hlan ahcun, dah hi nganpi ah um khawh:

  • Cawlcanghnak cu biahalnak 20 an i, na duh khawh zat in caan na lak khawh lai.
  • Cawlcanghnak tuah awk a herh ruangah na lungthin dihlak in na pek khawhnak ding hmun dai a um awk.
  • Na herh ahcun biahalnak kha na hrial khawh, asinain biahalnak pakhat cio kha na phi pek khawh i zuam awk.
  • Cawlcanghnak cu voikhatnak ah lim in tuah khawh ve rawh.
cognitive_instructions_trial_step_1_text:
Screen pakhat cio ah '?' nih a langhter bantukin a tlaumi hmanthlak he grid na hmuh lai. Grid tang ah a dang muisam pali an um, cu hna lak ah pakhat nih '?' grid lim khawhnak ding caah.

Cawnnak aa thawk tik ah, a dihmi grid pakhat cio tang ah a ummi muisam kha thim law, a dang biahalnak ah kal awkah 'Confirm' kha hmet.

Biahalnak kha 'Skip' hmet in na hrial khawh. Na timh cia tikah, 'View Example' kha hmet law tahchunhnak pakhat hmuh khawh a si.
cognitive_instructions_trial_step_4_time:
• Biahalnak 20 cio he cawlcanghnak phun hnih na hmuh lai. A hmasa bik set caah, na tuah khawh tawk biahalnak tuah awkah minutes 5 caan pek na si lai. A pahnihnak caah, caan khiahmi a um lai lo. Na duh zat in caan na lak khawh lai.
  • Lungretheihnak um loin cawlcanghnak hna kha na lungthin dihlak in na pek khawhnak ding hmun dai tein na kawl awk a si.
  • Na herh ahcun biahalnak kha na hrial khawh, asinain biahalnak pakhat cio kha a phi pek khawh i zuam.
  • Zaangfahnak tein cawlcanghnak pahnih kha voikhat tthutnak ah lim.

A tu cu a voikhatnak exercise tuah caan a si cang.

Biahalnak na tuah khawh tawk leh awkah minutes 5 na ngei lai ti kha philh hlah.

Hi hnu a, biahalnak pawl chungin a hmanrawh.

Min. 5 min cu thil pawl hna kha na hmanhnak pawl chungin hrial khawh.
cognitive_instructions_trial_step_4_unti:
• Na biahalnak hna a 20 biahalnak hna cu tuah khawh rawh. Hmasa hnih set tuah caan a, a duhmi a theihchhan hna kha, a tthut ahcun a cung a hleih khawh ve maw. Hmasa bik set tuah caan a, hmanhnak zung a phan 5 miin a kan i laih tthut a si.
  • Na thil pawl hna a hmanhrawh loh mi mhuahin pawl chungin ihrial khawh caah, mthia pawl kha a khua hman.
  • Na hngalhmi hna a lak khawh ti tnguh pawl kha, a si maw, hna biahalnak hna zawng chungin hrial khawh.
  • Hmasahin hna pawl a hmanhnak pawl hna mi kah hmanrawh po mi pawl hna kha philhrawh a si.

Uhnak a, pawl ti maw hna Hmasahnih oki

Tu cu a hman hnihnak cawlcanghnak tuahnak caan a si...

Na tuah khawh tawk biahalnak cu na duh zat in caan na lak khawh lai ti kha ngan aw.

cognitive_practice_step_1_text: Hi grid ah, row pakhat chungin hmawhtlawm hriamhmi shape 180 degree ah thil khawh i, a cunglei cell ah i phan khawh. Grid cu a phan khawh shape cu cunglei hmun pawl ah bawmhmi.
cognitive_practice_step_2_text: Hi grid ah, thil pawl a hmanhrawh loh zung pawl cu thil pawl chungin hmi 1 hrial khawh. A pungkhat hmanhnak pawl a zungh nahkawh laih krah. A hmanhnak pawl a phihnungmi pawl a hmanrawh khawh a si.
cognitive_practice_step_3_text: Top row ah, a tungkau hma a um mi thilri cu hngalh bik in a chung iangin a pianzia a si tawn. A pumpak a ummi hrawng le rang cu paih khawh thlun hnawk in tuak caah a ngil leu. A leltawhmi lehlam le tawlam cu a ngaih hnawhmi tiangin kan nei.
